data.description:
OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED DUE TO WEATHER Text or call agent for showings 26 crossed fenced acres for your 2 legged and 4 legged friends. Too many things to list, must see! 4 bed 2 bath brick home with all amenities, including a peaceful back deck overlooking the property where the deer roam. Stalled barn with one stall ready for chickens, and hay loft up top.

Tenant to take care of all property at all times. Tenant pays electric, on well and septic. $40 app fee PER applicant, $1700 deposit. Pets will be considered on a per animal basis.
